profile:
Crose Mechanical is a full service Mechanical, Heating, Ventilation, and Air Conditioning company with 25 years of experience serving
Owen Sound, Grey and Bruce. Offering Sales, Service, Repair and Maintenance of affordable Heating and Cooling solutions. We offer free estimates and look forward to hearing from you. Now with Office & Showroom - Stop in for a coffee - 2020 20th St E Unit 1, Owen Sound.
services: Furnaces, Boilers, Fireplaces, Space Heating, Heat Pumps and Air Conditioning. Commercial troubleshooting expertise. Mechanical Maintenance for Commercial and Residential properties. Crose Mechanical also offers extended warranty packages at affordable monthly or yearly rates.
